## Assistant Interoperability
- Treat SDD artifacts and Make targets as the canonical contract across all assistants.
- Assistants MUST default to SDD-enabled execution unless the user explicitly opts out in the current request.
- Codex skill bundles under `.agents/skills/**` are optional accelerators; they do not replace governance.
- If an assistant cannot load Codex skills directly, follow the corresponding `SKILL.md` files as runbooks and execute the same repository commands.
